title: Agenda Free
description:
Swagu and Perk dive into the NBA being run by mostly international players, and how the faces of the league are changing amidst a heated MVP race between Nikola Jokic and Joel Embiid, also they discuss why the Phoenix Suns are winning so much despite injuries to young stars. Plus, they take a look at their favorite moments so far from the NCAA tournament.
